{
  "name": "CONCLUSION-page",
  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "name": "ConclusionPanel",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "ConclusionHeading",
          "html": "<h3>Conclusions</h3>"
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "ConclusionText",
          "html": "<p>The last survey section deals with the last station of {CmpnName}'s LP/GOLPP journey &mdash; either {genderObjectPronoun} current state of health or {genderObjectPronoun} state of health when {genderSubjectPronoun} crossed over the Rainbow Bridge.</p><p>These are difficult questions to answer, but they're also the most important ones. This section references the questions you answered earlier to help draw conclusions about the progression of {CmpnName}'s LP/GOLPP since {genderSubjectPronoun} first showed symptoms. If it's too painful to revisit this stage of {CmpnName}'s life, it might be best to discontinue the survey and return to it later if you choose to do so.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "ConclusionIntro",
          "html": "<p><b>NOTE:</b> The questions in this final section pertain to {CmpnName} {blobText}:</p>"
        },  

        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionDetailsPanel",
          "elements": [


            {
              "type": "checkbox",
              "name": "ConclusionsLimitations",
              "title": "Please describe any special considerations in place for {CmpnName} due to LP-related breathing issues:",
              "isRequired": true,
              "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "EXERCISE",
                  "text": "Exercise limitations"
                },
                {
                  "value": "FOOD",
                  "text": "Type, amount or frequency of feeding"
                },
                {
                  "value": "TRAVEL",
                  "text": "Travel restrictions"
                },
                {
                  "value": "EXCITEMENT",
                  "text": "Limit activities that cause excitement"
                }
              ],
              "showOtherItem": true
            },
            {
              "type": "checkbox",
              "name": "ConclusionsPolyneuropathy",
              "title": "Please describe {CmpnName}'s polyneuropathy:",
              "isRequired": true,
              "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "NO_SYMPTOMS",
                  "text": "No noticeable symptoms"
                },
                {
                  "value": "HIND_END",
                  "text": "Significant hind-end weakness"
                },
                {
                  "value": "FALLING",
                  "text": "Frequent falling"
                },
                {
                  "value": "GET_UP",
                  "text": "Difficulty getting up or standing"
                },
                {
                  "value": "URINARY",
                  "text": "Urinary incontinence"
                },
                {
                  "value": "FECAL",
                  "text": "Fecal incontinence"
                }
              ],
              "showOtherItem": false
            },
            {
              "type": "rating",
              "name": "ConclusionsQOL",
              "title": "How would you rate {CmpnName}'s quality of life at this stage?",
              "description": "1 = very poor, 3 = fair, 5 = very good",
              "isRequired": true,
              "rateValues": [
                { "value": 1, "text": "1" },
                { "value": 2, "text": "2" },
                { "value": 3, "text": "3" },
                { "value": 4, "text": "4" },
                { "value": 5, "text": "5" },
                { "value": "DONT_KNOW", "text": "Don't know" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },


        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionOtherConditionsPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
            "type": "checkbox",
            "name": "EarlyOtherConditions",
            "title": "What other conditions {doTense} {CmpnName} have at this stage?",
            "required": true,
            "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "GERD",
                  "text": "Acid reflux (GERD)"
                },
                {
                  "value": "ME",
                  "text": "Megaesophagus"
                },
                {
                  "value": "DM",
                  "text": "Degenerative Myelopathy"
                },
                {
                  "value": "ARTHRITIS",
                  "text": "Arthritis"
                },
                {
                  "value": "CUSHINGS",
                  "text": "Cushings"
                },
                {
                  "value": "CT",
                  "text": "Collapsing Trachea"
                },
                {
                  "value": "HYPOTHYROID",
                  "text": "Hypothyroidism"
                },
                {
                  "value": "HEMANGIOSARCOMA",
                  "text": "Hemangiosarcoma"
                }
              ],
              "choicesOrder": "none",
              "otherText": "Other (max. 250 characters)",
              "showOtherItem": true
            }
          ]
        },







        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionCauseOfDeathPanel",
          "title": "The Last Question",
          "visibleIf": "{LifeStatus} = true",
          "elements": [
              {
                "type": "html",
                "name": "ConclusionCauseOfDeathHeading",
                "html": "Humane euthanasia is how most people choose to say goodbye to their beloved companions when their quality of life reaches a point where letting them go is in their best interest. This last question asks about why {CmpnName}'s quality of life reached that point. "
              },
              {
                "type": "radiogroup",
                "name": "ConclusionCauseOfDeath",
                "title": "What was the ultimate reason why {CmpnName} crossed over the Rainbow Bridge?",
                "isRequired": true,
                "choices": [
                  {
                    "value": "CANCER",
                    "text": "Cancer"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "INFECTION",
                    "text": "Bacterial/viral infection"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "BREATHING_CRISIS",
                    "text": "Breathing crisis"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "ADVANCED_POLYNEUROPATHY",
                    "text": "Polyneuropathy/cognitive decline"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "COMPLICATIONS",
                    "text": "Direct post-operative complications of LP surgery or stent implant"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "NOT_SAY",
                    "text": "Prefer not to say"
                  }

                ],
                "showOtherItem": true,
                "otherText": "Other issues"
            }
          ]
        }











      ]
    }
  ]
}